data.description: This nestled bungalow is the perfect home for anyone looking for turn-key ready. Located in St. Johns this home is complete with bamboo floors and main level living. Kitchen includes brand-new stainless steel appliances, new cabinets, brand-new quartz countertops and vinyl floors. The dining room with sliding glass door out to your fully fenced spacious backyard. Two bedrooms and one updated bathroom on the main level. Make way into your basement with family room, additional bedroom and laundry complete with washer and dryer. With this property you have to option to completely enclose the lot with the manual gated driveway. Great location and only 15 minutes from downtown and minutes to Kenton, University Park and Pier Park. [Home Energy Score = 1. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10187558]
